- a password maker/generator interaction
- login -> landing page

- login :
  - pick a username
  - requirements (normal : at least 5 characters, 1 upper case, 1 number, 1 special)

  - pick a password :
  - first requirements being normal :
    - at least 8 characters
    - 1 upper case
    - 1 number
    - 1 special
    
    - fun ones :
        - require :
        - 1 more upper case
        - 1 more upper case for good luck
        - numbers should add up to something
        - numbers cannot include 6 or 7
        - include a month of the year
        - must include : (the word apple)
            the precise lexical identifier of the universally recognizable pomological specimen, typically exhibiting a red or green chromatic range and classified within the species Malus domestica, which, according to culturally propagated and scientifically unverified anecdotal accounts, is said to have descended upon the cranial region of a historically eminent English-born natural philosopher, mathematician, astronomer, and alchemist of the 17th–18th century scientific milieu, namely an individual of notable scholarly repute within the early Royal Society tradition, whose contributions to classical mechanics and the mathematical description of universal gravitation have been extensively documented, thereby purportedly contributing to his subsequent theoretical articulation of gravitational force.
        
        - other
    
    - confirm password 

    - traitement (fake visual)
        - message : weak password, or not suitable
        - would you like to generate a strong one ?

        - generator
        - confirm
    
    - landing page :
        - display of the most inspiring popular designers and developpers portfolios
        - cool display, sections, follows their theme and AD
        - include their links  

    - make the presentation more immersive, more visual, more matching

    - more password requirements :

    - Digits must be in ascending order.
    - Must contain today's year.
    - Password length must be a prime number.
    - Password length must equal the number of vowels × 4.
    - Every special character must be surrounded by vowels.
    - Must contain a country bordering France.
    - Must contain a Git command
    
    - Must include your favorite color. (The game never tells you what it thinks your favorite color is.)
    - A timer counts down, but every satisfied rule adds 5 seconds.
